                <p>User feedback forms the basis of this stage. We gather the feedback given by those who interacted with the prototype and use it to develop the MVP. The MVP team refines the product to match the needs and preferences of the users and also fixes bugs in the initial version. The MVP product is now ready to launch to the early adopters.</p>
